Zachary Davis was 15 when he bludgeoned his mother Melanie Davis to death with a sledgehammer in August 2012 . 
  He then set his family home on fire and tried to kill his brother Josh with the same weapon . 
  On Tuesday he confessed to police that he laughed as he killed his mother . 
  He said his mother knew he was raped by his brother but did nothing about it . 
  Davis is on trial for first-degree murder and attempted murder of his brother . 
  His legal team say he was suffering from mental illness at the time of the attack . 
 